WEBVTT

00:05:29.553 --> 00:05:32.423
They take time beyond their school day,

00:05:32.447 --> 00:05:33.744
and come in on weekends

00:05:33.768 --> 00:05:38.221
and even use their own money
to often provide resources

00:05:38.921 --> 00:05:40.624
when we do not have it.

00:05:41.804 --> 00:05:43.652
And as the principal,

00:05:43.676 --> 00:05:46.562
I have to inspect what I expect.

00:05:47.308 --> 00:05:49.157
So I show up in classes

00:05:49.836 --> 00:05:52.922
and I conduct observations
to give feedback,

00:05:52.946 --> 00:05:56.361
because I want my teachers
to be just as successful

00:05:56.385 --> 00:05:58.700
as the name Mott Hall Bridges Academy.

00:05:59.930 --> 00:06:03.622
And I give them access to me
every single day,